#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"New to the corp or to EVE? Our veterans will fly with you and show you the "
"ropes — from your first overview setup to your first fleet kill. Sign up as "
"a cadet, get paired with a mentor, and work through hands-on field exercises "
"at your own pace."
msgstr ""
"Neu in der Corp oder bei EVE? Unsere Veteranen fliegen mit dir und zeigen "
"dir die Grundlagen — vom ersten Overview-Setup bis zum ersten Fleet-Kill. "
"Melde dich als Kadett an, werde einem Mentor zugeteilt und arbeite "
"praxisnahe Feldübungen in deinem eigenen Tempo durch."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Welcome to the Corporation"
msgstr "Willkommen in der Corporation"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "EVE Client & Overview Setup"
msgstr "EVE-Client & Overview-Setup"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Travel, Safety & Survival"
msgstr "Reise, Sicherheit & Überleben"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Ship Fitting & Doctrine Basics"
msgstr "Schiffs-Fitting & Doctrine-Grundlagen"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "PvP Basics"
msgstr "PvP-Grundlagen"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Fleet Operations"
msgstr "Fleet-Operationen"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Logistics & Buyback Services"
msgstr "Logistik- & Buyback-Services"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Manufacturing & Industry"
msgstr "Fertigung & Industrie"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
