msgstr "Skill-Planung"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get plugged into comms, people and the way we do things."
msgstr "Finde Anschluss an Comms, Leute und unsere Arbeitsweise."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make the client actually readable — overview, brackets, windows."
msgstr "Mach den Client wirklich lesbar — Overview, Brackets, Fenster."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get where you're going and come back alive."
msgstr "Komm ans Ziel und kehr lebend zurück."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand slots, tank, and why a doctrine fit is a doctrine fit."
msgstr "Verstehe Slots, Tank und warum ein Doctrine-Fit ein Doctrine-Fit ist."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make ISK from rats without feeding your ship to a roam."
msgstr "Mach ISK mit Rats, ohne dein Schiff einem Roam zu opfern."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pull ore, compress it, and feed the buyback."
msgstr "Bau Erz ab, komprimiere es und beliefere den Buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Scan it down, hack it, and get out clean."
msgstr "Scann es runter, hack es und komm sauber raus."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Tackle, hold point, follow the FC, and learn from the mail."
msgstr "Tackle, halt den Point, folge dem FC und lerne aus dem Mail."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Anchor, align, broadcast — be an asset in a fleet."
msgstr "Anchor, align, broadcast — sei eine Bereicherung für die Fleet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Move things and turn loot into ISK, the corp way."
msgstr "Bewege Fracht und mach aus Loot ISK — auf die Corp-Art."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Blueprints, ME/TE, and installing your first job."
msgstr "Blueprints, ME/TE und das Installieren deines ersten Jobs."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Train the right skills in the right order."
msgstr "Trainiere die richtigen Skills in der richtigen Reihenfolge."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Read the corp rules & culture"
msgstr "Lies die Regeln & Kultur der Corp"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Set up Discord / Mumble comms"
msgstr "Discord-/Mumble-Comms einrichten"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn who the officers & FCs are"
msgstr "Lerne, wer die Offiziere & FCs sind"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand corp services (SRP, buyback, logistics, doctrines)"
msgstr "Verstehe die Corp-Services (SRP, Buyback, Logistik, Doctrines)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Link your character & grant baseline ESI"
msgstr "Verknüpfe deinen Charakter & gewähre grundlegenden ESI-Zugriff"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Have your first onboarding chat with your mentor"
msgstr "Führe dein erstes Onboarding-Gespräch mit deinem Mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure your overview"
msgstr "Konfiguriere dein Overview"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure brackets & the tactical display"
msgstr "Konfiguriere die Brackets & das taktische Display"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Lay out local, d-scan and the fleet window"
msgstr "Ordne Local, D-Scan und das Fleet-Fenster an"

