#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
#, python-format
msgid "An extraction planet self-refining into %(name)s (%(tier)s)"
msgstr "Ein Extraktionsplanet, der selbst zu %(name)s (%(tier)s) veredelt"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
#, python-format
msgid "A factory planet buying inputs to make %(name)s (%(tier)s)"
msgstr ""
"Ein Fabrikplanet, der Inputs kauft, um %(name)s (%(tier)s) herzustellen"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
#, python-format
msgid "nets about %(isk)s ISK/day per planet at current prices"
msgstr "bringt zu aktuellen Preisen netto etwa %(isk)s ISK/Tag pro Planet"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
#, python-format
msgid "and you already have the planets for it (%(planets)s)"
msgstr "und du hast die Planeten dafür bereits (%(planets)s)"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
#, python-format
msgid "if you can extract from %(planets)s"
msgstr "wenn du von %(planets)s fördern kannst"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
msgid "Corp priority"
msgstr "Corp-Priorität"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
msgid "Best profit"
msgstr "Bester Gewinn"

#: apps/planetary/recommend.py
msgid "Beginner recommended"
msgstr "Für Einsteiger empfohlen"

#: apps/planetary/services.py
msgid "No live colony of this type imported yet."
msgstr "Noch keine Live-Kolonie dieses Typs importiert."

#: apps/planetary/services.py
msgid "Your live colony is pulling a different product than the plan expects."
msgstr "Deine Live-Kolonie fördert ein anderes Produkt, als der Plan erwartet."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "The all-rounder. Great first planet."
msgstr "Der Allrounder. Toller erster Planet."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Balanced and forgiving — food, industrial and electronics feedstock. If "
"you're new, start here."
msgstr ""
"Ausgewogen und gutmütig — Rohstoffe für Nahrung, Industrie und Elektronik. "
"Wenn du neu bist, fang hier an."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Robotics & electronics feedstock."
msgstr "Rohstoffe für Robotik & Elektronik."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Reliable all-rounder rich in metals and organics. Backbone of most "
"electronics and robotics chains."
msgstr ""
"Zuverlässiger Allrounder, reich an Metallen und Organik. Rückgrat der "
"meisten Elektronik- und Robotik-Ketten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Construction metals & heavy industry."
msgstr "Baumetalle & Schwerindustrie."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Metals and magma — the source of construction materials and many high-end "
"refined commodities."
msgstr ""
"Metalle und Magma — die Quelle für Baumaterialien und viele hochwertige "
"veredelte Waren."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "High-end electronics & metals."
msgstr "High-End-Elektronik & Metalle."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Harsh but valuable: heavy metals and non-CS crystals that feed advanced "
"electronics and superconductors."
msgstr ""
"Rau, aber wertvoll: Schwermetalle und Nicht-CS-Kristalle, die "
"fortschrittliche Elektronik und Supraleiter speisen."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Coolant, life-support & fuels."
msgstr "Kühlmittel, Lebenserhaltung & Treibstoffe."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Cold storage of gases, water and microorganisms — coolant, oxygen and "
"biotech chains start here."
msgstr ""
"Kühllager für Gase, Wasser und Mikroorganismen — Kühlmittel-, Sauerstoff- "
"und Biotech-Ketten beginnen hier."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Fuels, oxidisers & industrials."
msgstr "Treibstoffe, Oxidatoren & Industriegüter."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"The only source of Reactive Gas. Gas planets drive oxidising compounds, "
"oxygen and fuel chains."
msgstr ""
"Die einzige Quelle für Reactive Gas. Gasplaneten liefern oxidierende "
"Verbindungen, Sauerstoff und Treibstoffketten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Biotech & strong food chains."
msgstr "Biotech & starke Nahrungsketten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Water-rich and organic — the best planet for biomass, proteins and the "
"biotech P3/P4 lines."
msgstr ""
"Wasserreich und organisch — der beste Planet für Biomasse, Proteine und die "
"Biotech-P3/P4-Linien."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Electronics feedstock (plasmoids)."
msgstr "Elektronik-Ausgangsmaterial (Plasmoids)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Electrically charged: plasmoids, ionic solutions and noble gas for the "
"electronics and superconductor chains."
msgstr ""
"Elektrisch geladen: Plasmoids, Ionic Solutions und Noble Gas für die "
"Elektronik- und Supraleiterketten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Extraction planet"
msgstr "Extraktionsplanet"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Pull one or two raw P0 resources and refine them on-site into P1 (or "
"straight P2 if you have the feedstock)."
msgstr ""
"Fördere ein oder zwei rohe P0-Ressourcen und veredle sie vor Ort zu P1 (oder "
"direkt zu P2, wenn du die Vorprodukte hast)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (sets your power/CPU budget — upgrade it fully)."
msgstr "1× Command Center (legt dein Power/CPU-Budget fest — voll ausbauen)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"1× Extractor Control Unit per resource, with as many extractor heads as CPU/"
"PG allows (more heads = more yield, but shorter reach)."
msgstr ""
"1× Extractor Control Unit pro Ressource, mit so vielen Extractor-Heads, wie "
"CPU/PG zulassen (mehr Heads = mehr Ertrag, aber kürzere Reichweite)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Basic Industry Facilities to convert P0 → P1 (each does 3,000 P0 → 20 P1 "
"every 30 min)."
msgstr ""
"Basic Industry Facilities, um P0 → P1 umzuwandeln (jede schafft alle 30 Min. "
"3.000 P0 → 20 P1)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad as the export point and buffer storage."
msgstr "1× Launchpad als Exportpunkt und Pufferlager."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Route extractor output → storage/launchpad → factories → launchpad. Keep the "
"extracted P0 flowing into the BIFs and the finished P1 to the launchpad for "
"export."
msgstr ""
"Route: Extractor-Output → Storage/Launchpad → Factories → Launchpad. Sorge "
"dafür, dass das geförderte P0 stetig in die BIFs läuft und das fertige P1 "
"zum Export auf dem Launchpad landet."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export P1 (or P2) via the customs office. Import nothing."
msgstr "Exportiere P1 (oder P2) über das Customs Office. Importiere nichts."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import cheaper lower-tier materials and refine them up a tier. No extraction "
"— pure manufacturing throughput."
msgstr ""
"Importiere billigere Materialien niedrigerer Stufe und veredle sie eine "
"Stufe höher. Keine Förderung — reiner Fertigungsdurchsatz."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (upgrade fully for CPU/PG)."
msgstr "1× Command Center (für CPU/PG voll ausbauen)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad to receive imports and hold exports."
msgstr "1× Launchpad, um Importe entgegenzunehmen und Exporte zu lagern."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"As many Advanced Industry Facilities as your power/CPU allows (each does "
"40+40 input → 5 output every hour for P2)."
msgstr ""
"So viele Advanced Industry Facilities, wie dein Power/CPU zulässt (jede "
"schafft bei P2 stündlich 40+40 Input → 5 Output)."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities to buffer inputs between imports."
msgstr "Storage Facilities, um Inputs zwischen den Importen zu puffern."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import inputs to the launchpad → route to each factory → route finished "
"goods back to the launchpad."
msgstr ""
"Importiere Inputs zum Launchpad → route sie zu jeder Factory → route die "
"fertigen Waren zurück zum Launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Import the P1/P2 inputs; export the higher-tier product."
msgstr "Importiere die P1/P2-Inputs; exportiere das Produkt der höheren Stufe."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage / staging planet"
msgstr "Lager-/Staging-Planet"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A buffer or consolidation point. Rare for most pilots — usually a launchpad "
"on another planet does the job."
msgstr ""
"Ein Puffer oder Sammelpunkt. Für die meisten Piloten selten nötig — meist "
"reicht ein Launchpad auf einem anderen Planeten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center"
msgstr "1× Command Center"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad"
msgstr "1× Launchpad"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities as needed."
msgstr "Storage Facilities nach Bedarf."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Consolidate goods here before a single haul out."
msgstr "Sammle die Waren hier, bevor du sie in einem Rutsch raushaulst."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export in bulk on your haul day."
msgstr "Exportiere gesammelt an deinem Haul-Tag."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Not upgrading the Command Center"
msgstr "Das Command Center nicht upgraden"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Your Command Center level sets your entire CPU/PG budget. Upgrade it to "
"level 5 before you place facilities, or you'll run out of power halfway "
"through."
msgstr ""
"Die Stufe deines Command Centers bestimmt dein gesamtes CPU-/PG-Budget. "
"Bring es auf Stufe 5, bevor du Einrichtungen platzierst — sonst geht dir auf "
"halber Strecke der Strom aus."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Routing errors"
msgstr "Routing-Fehler"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A facility with no inbound route sits idle; a route to the wrong storage "
"stalls the chain. Follow every product from extractor → factory → launchpad."
msgstr ""
"Eine Facility ohne eingehende Route steht still; eine Route in die falsche "
"Storage legt die Kette lahm. Verfolge jedes Produkt vom Extractor → Factory "
"→ Launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Too many extractor heads"
msgstr "Zu viele Extractor-Heads"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"More heads raise yield but shorten the extraction radius and cost CPU/PG. "
"Balance heads against the program length you actually want to run."
msgstr ""
"Mehr Heads erhöhen den Ertrag, verkürzen aber den Extraktionsradius und "
"kosten CPU/PG. Wäge die Zahl der Heads gegen die Programmlaufzeit ab, die du "
"wirklich fahren willst."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Insufficient storage"
msgstr "Zu wenig Lagerplatz"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"If a launchpad or storage fills up, upstream facilities stop. Size storage "
"for the time between your resets."
msgstr ""
"Läuft ein Launchpad oder eine Storage voll, stoppen die vorgelagerten "
"Facilities. Dimensioniere die Storage für die Zeit zwischen deinen Resets."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wrong schematic"
msgstr "Falsches Schematic"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Setting a factory to the wrong schematic wastes materials. Double-check "
"inputs match what you're actually routing in."
msgstr ""
"Ein falsches Schematic in der Factory verschwendet Material. Prüf nach, dass "
"die Inputs zu dem passen, was du tatsächlich hineinroutest."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Overbuilding factories"
msgstr "Zu viele Factories bauen"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Ten factories starved of feedstock earn less than three that run "
"continuously. Match factory count to your extraction rate."
msgstr ""
"Zehn Factories ohne Nachschub bringen weniger ein als drei, die durchgehend "
"laufen. Richte die Zahl der Factories an deiner Förderrate aus."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Ignoring customs (POCO) tax"
msgstr "Die Customs-Office-Steuer (POCO) ignorieren"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Export/import tax at the customs office is charged on every launch. In "
"hostile space it can dwarf your margin — factor it in before you commit."
msgstr ""
"Die Export-/Importsteuer am Customs Office fällt bei jedem Start an. In "
"feindlichem Space kann sie deine Marge auffressen — rechne sie ein, bevor du "
"dich festlegst."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Train Command Center Upgrades to unlock the planet tiers you need."
msgstr ""
"Trainiere Command Center Upgrades, um die Planeten-Tiers freizuschalten, die "
"du brauchst."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Buy and deploy a Command Center on each planet, then upgrade it fully."
msgstr ""
"Kauf und deploye auf jedem Planeten ein Command Center und upgrade es "
"vollständig."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "On extraction planets: place the ECU, add heads, and start a program."
msgstr ""
"Auf Extraktionsplaneten: ECU platzieren, Heads setzen und ein Programm "
"starten."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Place your factories and set the correct schematic on each."
msgstr ""
"Platziere deine Factories und stelle bei jeder das richtige Schematic ein."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wire the routes: extractor → storage → factory → launchpad."
msgstr "Leg die Routen: Extractor → Storage → Factory → Launchpad."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Confirm the customs office tax for your space and your standings."
msgstr ""
"Prüf die Steuer des Customs Office für deinen Space und deine Standings."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Set a reset cadence that matches your extractor program length."
msgstr ""
"Leg einen Reset-Rhythmus fest, der zur Laufzeit deines Extractor-Programms "
"passt."

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Haul exports to your chosen market hub (or hand to corp buyback)."
msgstr ""
"Haul die Exporte zu deinem Markt-Hub (oder gib sie in den Corp-Buyback)."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing planets"
msgstr "Fehlende Planeten"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Not costed"
msgstr "Nicht kalkuliert"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing prices"
msgstr "Fehlende Preise"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Unprofitable"
msgstr "Unrentabel"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Profitable"
msgstr "Rentabel"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "The Planetary Industry planner is currently disabled by leadership."
msgstr "Der Planetary-Industry-Planer ist derzeit von der Führung deaktiviert."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Add at least one planet — that's what the plan is built around."
msgstr "Füge mindestens einen Planeten hinzu — darauf baut der Plan auf."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Each factory planet needs a product to build — pick one."
msgstr "Jeder Fabrikplanet braucht ein Produkt zum Bauen — wähle eines aus."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Plan “%(name)s” created — here's your setup and profit estimate."
msgstr ""
"Plan “%(name)s” erstellt — hier sind dein Setup und deine Profitschätzung."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Plan updated and re-costed."
msgstr "Plan aktualisiert und neu kalkuliert."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Keep at least one planet on the plan."
msgstr "Behalte mindestens einen Planeten im Plan."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Re-costed with the latest market prices."
msgstr "Neu kalkuliert mit den aktuellen Marktpreisen."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Duplicated as “%(name)s”."
msgstr "Dupliziert als “%(name)s”."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Status set to %(status)s."
msgstr "Status auf %(status)s gesetzt."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” archived. Delete again to remove it permanently."
msgstr "“%(name)s” archiviert. Erneut löschen, um ihn endgültig zu entfernen."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” permanently deleted."
msgstr "“%(name)s” endgültig gelöscht."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "A colony sync is already running — give it a minute before retrying."
msgstr ""
"Ein Kolonie-Sync läuft bereits — warte eine Minute, bevor du es erneut "
"versuchst."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Colony sync queued for %(count)s pilot(s) — refresh in a minute."
msgstr ""
"Kolonie-Sync für %(count)s Pilot(en) eingereiht — in einer Minute "
"aktualisieren."

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Grant the Planetary Industry scope first, then sync your colonies."
msgstr ""
"Gewähre zuerst den Planetary-Industry-Scope, dann synchronisiere deine "
"Kolonien."

#: apps/raffle/contest_templates.py
