#, python-format
msgid "config v%(version)s"
msgstr "Config v%(version)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#, python-format
msgid "last by %(by)s"
msgstr "zuletzt von %(by)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Calibration — what would be proposed for now"
msgstr "Kalibrierung — was derzeit vorgeschlagen würde"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"No measured outcomes yet — nothing is trusted, so autonomous proposal stays "
"silent even when armed. Trust accrues as accepted COAs complete and their "
"outcomes are measured."
msgstr ""
"Noch keine gemessenen Ergebnisse — nichts gilt als vertrauenswürdig, daher "
"bleibt der autonome Vorschlag still, selbst wenn er scharfgeschaltet ist. "
"Vertrauen wächst, sobald akzeptierte COAs abgeschlossen und ihre Ergebnisse "
"gemessen werden."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#, python-format
msgid "spread %(spread)s"
msgstr "Streuung %(spread)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "▲ trusted"
msgstr "▲ vertrauenswürdig"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "○ not yet"
msgstr "○ noch nicht"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Classification"
msgstr "Klassifizierung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Set the default report classification and the tier → minimum-role map that "
"gates who can read each tier. A <span class=\"text-cyan\">design floor</"
"span> is enforced server-side — a tier can be tightened but never loosened "
"below its built-in minimum."
msgstr ""
"Lege die Standard-Klassifizierung für Berichte und die Zuordnung Stufe → "
"Mindestrolle fest, die steuert, wer welche Stufe lesen darf. Eine <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">Design-Untergrenze</span> wird serverseitig erzwungen — "
"eine Stufe kann verschärft, aber nie unter ihr eingebautes Minimum gelockert "
"werden."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Default classification"
msgstr "Standard-Klassifizierung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "The tier a report falls back to when its template specifies none."
msgstr ""
"Die Stufe, auf die ein Bericht zurückfällt, wenn sein Template keine angibt."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Tier → minimum role"
msgstr "Stufe → Mindestrolle"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Restores the default classification and every tier floor to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr ""
"Setzt die Standard-Klassifizierung und jede Stufen-Untergrenze auf die "
"ausgelieferten Standardwerte zurück."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Constraints &amp; thresholds"
msgstr "Einschränkungen &amp; Schwellenwerte"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Tune the global severity ratios, demand baselines and which constraint "
"providers run. A threshold change re-colours severities on the <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">next snapshot</span> with no deploy. A net-new provider "
"stays disabled until you enable it here."
msgstr ""
"Passe die globalen Schweregrad-Verhältnisse, die Bedarfs-Baselines und die "
"laufenden Beschränkungs-Provider an. Eine Änderung eines Schwellenwerts "
"färbt die Schweregrade beim <span class=\"text-cyan\">nächsten Snapshot</"
"span> neu ein — ohne Deploy. Ein ganz neuer Provider bleibt deaktiviert, bis "
"du ihn hier aktivierst."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Global severity ratios"
msgstr "Globale Schweregrad-Verhältnisse"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Constraint providers"
msgstr "Beschränkungs-Provider"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "No constraint providers are registered."
msgstr "Es sind keine Beschränkungs-Provider registriert."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Demand targets"
msgstr "Bedarfsziele"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"One per line as <code class=\"text-faint\">key value</code> — e.g. <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>. Leave empty to seed "
"demand from data."
msgstr ""
"Eine pro Zeile als <code class=\"text-faint\">Schlüssel Wert</code> — z. B. "
"<code class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>. Leer lassen, um "
"den Bedarf aus den Daten zu speisen."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Restores every ratio, provider flag and demand target to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr ""
"Setzt jedes Verhältnis, jedes Provider-Flag und jedes Bedarfsziel auf die "
"ausgelieferten Standardwerte zurück."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Command Intelligence · Scheduled reports &amp; delivery · [FORCA] Command "
"Grid"
msgstr ""
"Kommandoaufklärung · Geplante Berichte &amp; Zustellung · [FORCA] Command "
"Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Scheduled reports &amp; delivery"
msgstr "Geplante Berichte &amp; Zustellung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"The weekly briefing generates in the background; delivery is <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">classification-aware</span> and ships <span class=\"text-"
"gold\">disarmed</span> — a director-eyes-only report can never be broadcast "
"to a corp-wide Discord channel (the server refuses that pairing). Nothing "
"leaves the server until you arm a channel and configure its target below."
msgstr ""
"Das wöchentliche Briefing wird im Hintergrund erzeugt; die Zustellung ist "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">klassifizierungsbewusst</span> und wird <span "
"class=\"text-gold\">inaktiv</span> ausgeliefert — ein Bericht nur für die "
"Augen der Direktoren kann niemals in einen corp-weiten Discord-Kanal "
"gesendet werden (der Server verweigert diese Kombination). Nichts verlässt "
"den Server, bis du einen Kanal scharfschaltest und unten sein Ziel "
"konfigurierst."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM enabled — scheduled briefings are narrated. (Without a key they still "
"generate a deterministic report.)"
msgstr ""
"LLM aktiviert — geplante Briefings werden narrativ ausformuliert. (Ohne Key "
"erzeugen sie weiterhin einen deterministischen Bericht.)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM disabled — scheduled briefings still generate the deterministic "
"constraint picture."
msgstr ""
"LLM deaktiviert — geplante Briefings erzeugen weiterhin das deterministische "
"Beschränkungsbild."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Scheduled generation"
msgstr "Geplante Erzeugung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Generate a weekly briefing"
msgstr "Wöchentliches Briefing erzeugen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Monday 12:00 UTC. Deduped against a recent run so a retried beat never "
"double-spends tokens."
msgstr ""
"Montag 12:00 UTC. Wird gegen einen kürzlichen Lauf dedupliziert, damit ein "
"wiederholter Beat niemals doppelt Token verbraucht."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Only announce when binding at/above"
msgstr "Nur ankündigen, wenn bindend auf/über"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Suppress delivery of a quiet report with no meaningful constraint."
msgstr ""
"Unterdrückt die Zustellung eines ruhigen Berichts ohne nennenswerte "
"Beschränkung."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Discord (broadcast)"
msgstr "Discord (Broadcast)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm Discord delivery"
msgstr "Discord-Zustellung scharfschalten"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Posts a classification-safe summary to every active Discord webhook "
"(configured under In-game Alerts)."
msgstr ""
"Postet eine klassifizierungssichere Zusammenfassung an jeden aktiven Discord-"
"Webhook (konfiguriert unter In-Game-Warnungen)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Broadcast these classifications"
msgstr "Diese Klassifizierungen senden"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Only corp-shareable tiers can be broadcast; director/alliance tiers are "
"never offered here."
msgstr ""
"Nur corp-weit freigebbare Stufen können gesendet werden; Direktor-/Allianz-"
"Stufen werden hier nie angeboten."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "EVE-mail (targeted to leadership)"
msgstr "EVE-mail (gezielt an die Führung)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm EVE-mail delivery"
msgstr "EVE-mail-Zustellung scharfschalten"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Sends an in-game mail to the mains behind the owner tags below. Needs a "
"sender character with the <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</"
"code> scope."
msgstr ""
"Sendet eine In-Game-Mail an die Mains hinter den unten aufgeführten Owner-"
"Tags. Benötigt einen Absender-Charakter mit dem Scope <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</code>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Mail these classifications"
msgstr "Diese Klassifizierungen per Mail senden"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Targeted mail may carry the sensitive tiers (it is not a broadcast)."
msgstr ""
"Gezielte Mail darf die sensiblen Stufen enthalten (sie ist kein Broadcast)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Sender character id"
msgstr "Absender-Charakter-ID"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"A corp character that granted the mail-send scope. Leave blank to disable."
msgstr ""
"Ein Corp-Charakter, der den Mail-Send-Scope gewährt hat. Leer lassen, um zu "
"deaktivieren."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Recipient owner tags"
msgstr "Owner-Tags der Empfänger"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Space- or comma-separated (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">strategic_director</code>). Their mains receive the mail."
msgstr ""
"Leerzeichen- oder kommagetrennt (z. B. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">strategic_director</code>). Ihre Mains erhalten die Mail."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Command Intelligence · Provider &amp; model · [FORCA] Command Grid"
msgstr "Command Intelligence · Provider &amp; Modell · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Provider &amp; model"
msgstr "Anbieter &amp; Modell"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Pick the runtime model name, output sizing, budgets and call discipline. The "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">API key</span> lives in the environment and is "
"never shown, edited or stored here — only its presence flips the subsystem "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Wähle den Namen des Laufzeitmodells, die Ausgabegröße, Budgets und die "
"Aufruf-Disziplin. Der <span class=\"text-cyan\">API-Schlüssel</span> liegt "
"in der Umgebung und wird hier nie angezeigt, bearbeitet oder gespeichert — "
"allein seine Anwesenheit schaltet das Subsystem ein."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Enabled — an <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> is present."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviert — ein <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> ist vorhanden."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Disabled — set <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> in the "
"environment to enable Command Intelligence."
msgstr ""
"Deaktiviert — setze <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> in der "
"Umgebung, um Command Intelligence zu aktivieren."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Model name"
msgstr "Modellname"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"The runtime model — overrides the env default (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> or <code class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M3</code>)."
msgstr ""
"Das Laufzeitmodell — überschreibt den Umgebungs-Standard (z. B. <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> oder <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M3</code>)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Max output tokens"
msgstr "Max. Ausgabe-Tokens"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Sized for reasoning plus the answer; raise on a length cut-off. Range 256–"
"65536."
msgstr ""
"Bemessen für Reasoning plus Antwort; bei Längen-Abbruch erhöhen. Bereich 256–"
"65536."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Temperature"
msgstr "Temperatur"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Sampling temperature, 0–1. Lower is more deterministic."
msgstr "Sampling-Temperatur, 0–1. Niedriger ist deterministischer."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Token budget per report"
msgstr "Token-Budget pro Bericht"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Hard cap on prompt + completion tokens for a single report."
msgstr ""
"Harte Obergrenze für Prompt- + Completion-Tokens eines einzelnen Berichts."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Monthly token ceiling"
msgstr "Monatliche Token-Obergrenze"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Safety cap on total tokens spent across all reports in a month."
msgstr "Sicherheitsgrenze für die Gesamt-Tokens aller Berichte eines Monats."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Rate limit / hour"
msgstr "Ratenlimit / Stunde"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Reports per hour — backs the breaker counter."
msgstr "Berichte pro Stunde — Grundlage des Breaker-Zählers."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Repair attempts"
msgstr "Reparaturversuche"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Schema / grounding re-prompts on invalid structured output. Range 0–5."
msgstr ""
"Schema-/Grounding-Nachfragen bei ungültiger strukturierter Ausgabe. Bereich "
"0–5."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Restores the model, budgets and call discipline to the shipped defaults."
msgstr ""
"Setzt Modell, Budgets und Aufruf-Disziplin auf die ausgelieferten "
"Standardwerte zurück."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Role mappings · Comms access · Admin"
msgstr "Rollenzuordnungen · Comms-Zugriff · Admin"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "← Access sync settings"
msgstr "← Zugriffs-Sync-Einstellungen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "External comms access"
msgstr "Externer Comms-Zugriff"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Role mappings"
msgstr "Rollenzuordnungen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid ""
"Each row maps a FORCA entitlement to one platform role/group.\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">This is the managed set</strong> — the sync "
"only ever grants or removes roles listed here;\n"
"  anything else on the server is untouchable. A mapping grants when a pilot "
"has the entitlement; it <em>removes</em>\n"
"  on loss only when its mode is <strong class=\"text-ink\">Authoritative</"
"strong>. New mappings stay in dry-run until you confirm them."
msgstr ""
"Jede Zeile ordnet eine FORCA-Berechtigung genau einer Plattform-Rolle/-"
"Gruppe zu.\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">Dies ist der verwaltete Satz</strong> — der "
"Sync gewährt oder entfernt ausschließlich die hier aufgeführten Rollen;\n"
"  alles andere auf dem Server bleibt unangetastet. Eine Zuordnung gewährt, "
"sobald ein Pilot die Berechtigung hat; sie <em>entfernt</em>\n"
"  bei Verlust nur dann, wenn ihr Modus <strong class=\"text-"
"ink\">Autoritativ</strong> ist. Neue Zuordnungen bleiben im Testlauf, bis du "
"sie bestätigst."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add a mapping"
msgstr "Zuordnung hinzufügen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "Platform"
msgstr "Plattform"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Entitlement"
msgstr "Berechtigung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. Discord role id"
msgstr "z. B. Discord-Rollen-ID"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. @Member"
msgstr "z. B. @Member"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Target role id / name"
msgstr "Ziel-Rollen-ID / -Name"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Label (optional)"
msgstr "Label (optional)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_detail.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_sources.html
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "Modus"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Dry-run"
msgstr "Testlauf"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add mapping"
msgstr "Zuordnung hinzufügen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Mappings"
msgstr "Zuordnungen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "authoritative"
msgstr "autoritativ"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "additive"
msgstr "additiv"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "yes"
msgstr "ja"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "no"
msgstr "nein"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Remove this mapping? The sync will stop managing that role."
msgstr ""
"Diese Zuordnung entfernen? Der Sync verwaltet diese Rolle dann nicht mehr."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "No mappings yet. Until you add one, the sync manages nothing."
msgstr ""
"Noch keine Zuordnungen. Bis du eine hinzufügst, verwaltet der Sync nichts."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Comms access sync"
msgstr "Comms-Zugriffs-Sync"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Access sync settings"
msgstr "Zugriffs-Sync-Einstellungen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Linked accounts &amp; ledger"
msgstr "Verknüpfte Konten &amp; Logbuch"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This subsystem drives external-platform roles from corp membership + RBAC.\n"
"  It ships <strong class=\"text-ink\">inert</strong> and is configured "
"entirely here — no server\n"
"  access needed. To go live: <strong class=\"text-ink\">(1)</strong> enter "
"the Discord credentials,\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">(2)</strong> enable the feature, <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">(3)</strong> arm\n"
"  the platform, and <strong class=\"text-ink\">(4)</strong> take its\n"
"  <a href=\"%(mappings_url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">role "
"mappings</a>\n"
"  out of dry-run. The sync only ever touches roles that appear on the Role "
"mappings page."
msgstr ""
"Dieses Subsystem steuert Rollen auf externen Plattformen anhand von Corp-"
"Mitgliedschaft + RBAC.\n"
"  Es wird <strong class=\"text-ink\">inaktiv</strong> ausgeliefert und wird "
"vollständig hier konfiguriert — kein Server-\n"
"  Zugriff nötig. Zum Scharfschalten: <strong class=\"text-ink\">(1)</strong> "
"die Discord-Zugangsdaten eintragen,\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">(2)</strong> das Feature aktivieren, <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">(3)</strong> die Plattform\n"
"  scharfschalten und <strong class=\"text-ink\">(4)</strong> ihre\n"
"  <a href=\"%(mappings_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Rollenzuordnungen</a>\n"
"  aus dem Testlauf nehmen. Der Sync berührt ausschließlich Rollen, die auf "
"der Seite „Rollenzuordnungen“ erscheinen."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Discord credentials"
msgstr "Discord-Zugangsdaten"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid ""
"Create an application at the Discord Developer Portal. Add a bot with the\n"
"    <code>Manage Roles</code> permission and place its role <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">above</strong> every managed\n"
"    role. Secrets are encrypted at rest and never shown again — leave a "
"secret field blank to keep the current value."
msgstr ""
"Erstelle eine Anwendung im Discord Developer Portal. Füge einen Bot mit der "
"Berechtigung\n"
"    <code>Manage Roles</code> hinzu und platziere seine Rolle <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">über</strong> jeder verwalteten\n"
"    Rolle. Secrets werden verschlüsselt gespeichert und nie wieder angezeigt "
"— lass ein Secret-Feld leer, um den aktuellen Wert zu behalten."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Bot token"
msgstr "Bot-Token"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "•••••••• configured — leave blank to keep"
msgstr "•••••••• konfiguriert — zum Beibehalten leer lassen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "paste bot token"
msgstr "Bot-Token einfügen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Clear bot token"
msgstr "Bot-Token löschen"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Bot token configured"
msgstr "Bot-Token konfiguriert"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "(from env)"
msgstr "(aus der Umgebung)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "No bot token set"
msgstr "Kein Bot-Token gesetzt"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "OAuth client ID"
msgstr "OAuth-Client-ID"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "application client id"
msgstr "Client-ID der Anwendung"

