msgstr "Absender speichern"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/alerts.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Rules whose channels include <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> send "
"in-game from this director to the responsible officer, for <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">high</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">critical</span> "
"alerts. The chosen director must grant the <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> scope on the <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" "
"class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">ESI scopes</a> page — until then EVE-"
"mail degrades to a no-op."
msgstr ""
"Regeln, deren Kanäle <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> enthalten, "
"versenden bei <span class=\"text-ink\">hohen</span>/<span class=\"text-"
"ink\">kritischen</span> Warnungen In-Game-Mails von diesem Direktor an den "
"zuständigen Offizier. Der gewählte Direktor muss auf der Seite <a "
"href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">ESI-Scopes</a> "
"den Scope <span class=\"font-mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> gewähren — "
"bis dahin läuft EVE-mail ins Leere."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/alerts.html
