#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Readiness · Officer responsibilities"
msgstr "Einsatzbereitschaft · Offiziers-Zuständigkeiten"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid ""
"Map each dimension to an owner desk, and assign members to those desks. A "
"generated task routes to the first member on its desk; an unmapped dimension "
"leaves its tasks in the open claimable pool."
msgstr ""
"Ordne jeder Dimension ein verantwortliches Ressort zu und weise diesen "
"Ressorts Mitglieder zu. Eine erzeugte Aufgabe geht an das erste Mitglied "
"ihres Ressorts; bei einer nicht zugeordneten Dimension bleiben die Aufgaben "
"im offenen Pool zur Übernahme."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Owner desks"
msgstr "Verantwortliche Ressorts"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Desk label"
msgstr "Ressort-Bezeichnung"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
