"Asset Staging is <span class=\"text-cyan\">enabled</span> in the index — "
"adjust on <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"Asset-Staging ist im Index <span class=\"text-cyan\">aktiv</span> — anpassen "
"unter <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensionen &amp; Gewichtungen</a>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Scoring now, but <span class=\"text-ink\">not yet in the index</span> — "
"enable it on <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"Wird bereits bewertet, aber <span class=\"text-ink\">noch nicht im Index</"
"span> — aktiviere sie unter <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensionen &amp; Gewichtungen</a>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid ""
"No staging system set — choose one below. Until you do, the Asset Staging "
"dimension stays unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Kein Staging-System gesetzt — wähle unten eines aus. Bis dahin bleibt die "
"Dimension Asset-Staging nicht verfügbar."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
