msgstr "Staging-System speichern"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/strategic_roles.html
msgid ""
"Desired headcount per strategic role. The <span class=\"text-cyan\">Fleet "
"Composition</span>, <span class=\"text-cyan\">Strategic Assets</span> and "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">Leadership</span> dimensions score qualified "
"pilots against these targets. For <span class=\"text-ink\">By skills</span> "
"detection, set params like <code class=\"text-faint\">{\"skills\": "
"{\"3300\": 5}}</code> (skill type id → level); <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">manual</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">asset</span> targets are "
"tracked but not auto-counted yet."
msgstr ""
"Sollstärke je strategischer Rolle. Die Dimensionen <span class=\"text-"
"cyan\">Flottenzusammensetzung</span>, <span class=\"text-cyan\">Strategische "
"Assets</span> und <span class=\"text-cyan\">Leitung</span> messen "
"qualifizierte Piloten an diesen Zielen. Für die Erkennung <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">Nach Skills</span> setzt du Parameter wie <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">{\"skills\": {\"3300\": 5}}</code> (Skill-Typ-ID → Level); <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">manuelle</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">Asset</span>-"
"Ziele werden erfasst, aber noch nicht automatisch gezählt."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/strategic_roles.html
msgid "Role targets"
msgstr "Rollen-Ziele"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/strategic_roles.html
msgid ""
"No role targets yet. Add one below to start scoring fleet composition and "
"leadership depth."
msgstr ""
"Noch keine Rollen-Ziele. Füge unten eines hinzu, um Flottenzusammensetzung "
"und Führungstiefe zu bewerten."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/strategic_roles.html
