"The Fleet Support dimension is <span class=\"text-cyan\">enabled</span> and "
"contributes to the readiness index. Adjust this on <a href=\"%(url)s\" "
"class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"Die Dimension Flotten-Support ist <span class=\"text-cyan\">aktiv</span> und "
"fließt in den Einsatzbereitschafts-Index ein. Anpassen unter <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">Dimensionen &amp; "
"Gewichtungen</a>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
