"replaced. Each committed seed is listed so the redraw is fully on the record."
msgid_plural ""
"This contest was drawn more than once. The verified draw above is the one "
"that stands; the earlier draws below were discarded by leadership and "
"replaced. Each committed seed is listed so the redraw is fully on the record."
msgstr[0] ""
